Can you suggest 5 distinct themes that can be used for a rooftop bar that has a botanical-inspired atmosphere? Here is a PHP code that can be used to retrieve some ideas:
<?php
$themes = array("Tropical Oasis", "Garden in the Sky", "Jungle Hideaway", "Greenhouse Escape", "Wildflower Wonderland");
shuffle($themes);
for($i=0; $i<5; $i++) {
    echo ($i+1).". ".$themes[$i]."<br>";
}
?>
Feel free to modify the array with your own unique ideas!
